		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#96673d" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#96673d">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="255" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近地巡龙兽时，地巡龙兽原地旋转一圈，使用尾部齿轮造成<span color="#b9b9b9">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近地巡龙兽时，地巡龙兽使用头部进行挑击，向左向右各一次，每次造成<span color="#b9b9b9">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">离地巡龙兽较远时，地巡龙兽暴露头部弱点，扭头冲撞过来，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>伤害，若命中玩家则原地旋转一圈，再造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="428" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">地巡龙兽暴露头部弱点，使用两翼汲取元素力，向空中抛出13枚散弹，造成<span color="#bfbfff">100%,30%,10%</span><span>对应元素伤害并清空元素螺栓。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">地巡龙兽施放「散落洪流」后，会立即吸收元素填充<span textDecoration="underline">元素螺栓</span><span>，使下一次「散洪流落」技能附上元素伤害。瘫痪龙兽清空元素螺栓及提升的抗性。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
