		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="432" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">元素螺栓：储存元素力。以<span color="#ffebbf">上一次清空螺栓开始</span><span>所受到的</span><span color="#ff9999">总和最高</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffebbf">伤害属性</span><span>为准，</span><span color="#99ffcc">不吸收挂着的元素</span><span>，吸收完毕后该元素抗性</span><span color="#ff9999">+40%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
